article_title: Bernie Sanders draws big crowd in Minneapolis

article_metadata.description: The Bernie Sanders juggernaut rolled through Minneapolis yesterday. For MPR, Matt Sepic says, “Thousands of Bernie Sanders supporters lined up in Minneapolis Sunday morning to see the Vermont Senator who's running for president.

og.description: Plus: Medicaid enrollment in Minnesota soars; lawmaker wants law to address 'revenge porn'; Walker defends ultrasound law; and more.
og.title: Bernie Sanders draws big crowd in Minneapolis
